      "span_text": "The validated scoring system of the questionnaire was used to stratify patients into either \"low-risk\" or \"high-risk\" for having OSA. Subjects who scored positive in two or more categories were considered as \"high-risk\" for OAS, otherwise they were considered \"lowrisk\"."
